nterface elements on the page with just a few lines of code and an included CSS file. All the components in the Yahoo! User Interface Library have been released as open source under a BSD license and are free for all uses.", "imagename": "3711e9a9-e4c5-4d5d-8b7e-d7e2875ba167.gif", "infoid": 796, "category": "technology_design", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["yahoo", "interface", "library"]}, {"url": "http://www.youtube.com/w/Real-Transformer?v=dut6jxCiakg", "title": "YouTube - \u771f\u6b63\u7684\u53d8\u5f62\u91d1\u521a", "tags": "\u53d8\u5f62\u91d1\u521a \u89c6\u9891 ", "name": "alphanerd", "posttime": "2006-02-15 00:12:58", "ip": "202.196.64.100", "mark": 3, "note": "\u8fd9\u6bb5\u89c6\u9891\u5c55\u793a\u4e86\u4e00\u4e2a&quot;\u53d8\u5f62\u91d1\u521a&quot;\u673a\u5668\u4eba.", "imagename": "f4811fd8-ea04-4344-a5f5-c931044b3f02.jpg", "infoid": 795, "category": "technology_other", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["\u53d8\u5f62\u91d1\u521a", "\u89c6\u9891"]}, {"url": "http://newsvote.bbc.co.uk/chinese/simp/hi/newsid_4710000/newsid_4712600/4712672.stm", "title": "\u600c\u5a27\u595a\u00fb\"\u5bf9\u5065\u5eb7\u6709\u76ca\"", "tags": "\u540c\u6027\u604b \u5065\u5eb7 ", "name": "alphanerd", "posttime": "2006-02-15 00:05:16", "ip": "202.196.64.100", "mark": 1, "note": "\u753b\u8b1f\ufff4\u540c\u600c'&quot\u5a3b\u595a\u00fb&quot\u673b\u5209\u4ea9\u548e\u600c\u6027\u4e4b\u76ba\u8e84\u5fab\u50c3\u5e65\u30b7\u0002 \r\n\r\n\u4e0e\u5f02\u6027\u604b\u4eba\u76f8\u6bd4\uff0c\u540c\u6027\u604b\u793e\u533a\u91cc\u51fa\u73b0\u7684\u538b\u6291\uff0c\u5438\u6bd2\u548c\u60a3\u764c\u75c7\u7684\u6bd4\u4f8b\u8981\u9ad8\u3002", "imagename": "8e568aec-7f57-465b-8f3b-c663e19592b4.jpg", "infoid": 794, "category": "technology_other", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["\u540c\u